A warm, nostalgic vintage-style illustration showing two identical small green laptops with distinctive rounded edges and carrying handles, positioned like mirror images of each other. One laptop sits on a worn wooden desk in a cozy room with warm lamp light, while the other appears through a dreamy window-like portal surrounded by golden light, resting on red earth beneath a baobab tree silhouette. Soft sepia tones blend with pops of the laptops' bright green color. The composition suggests connection across distance, with subtle visual threads of light linking the two scenes. Faded paper texture overlay, muted color palette reminiscent of 1970s educational posters, with gentle vignetting around the edges.
